prompts.summarizer_user_template:
Read this paper and summarize it in English and return JSON only with keys: title, authors, affiliations, code_urls, problem, approach, methodological_novelty, empirical_novelty, tell_someone_in_4_5_sentences. The `title, authors, affiliations, code_urls` are simply obtained information fields from the paper. In the `problem` field, describe the problem the paper addresses in 1-3 sentences; in the `approach` field, describe the approach the paper takes in 1-2 sentences; in the `methodological_novelty` field, describe the novelty of the method in 1-2 sentences; in the `empirical_novelty` field, describe the novelty of the empirical evaluation in 1-2 sentences; and in the `tell_someone_in_4_5_sentences` field, tell the story of the paper in 4-5 sentences. 

Paper JSON:
{paper_json}
